=begin pod
=TITLE Gnome::Gtk4::R-TreeSortable
=head1 Description

The interface for sortable models used by GtkTreeView

L<Gnome::Gtk4::R-TreeSortable|/content-docs/api2/reference/Gtk4/R-TreeSortable> is an interface to be implemented by tree models which
support sorting. The L<Gnome::Gtk4::TreeView|/content-docs/api2/reference/Gtk4/TreeView> uses the methods provided by this interface
to sort the model.

