=head1 Signals

=comment -----------------------------------------------------------------------
=head3 sort-column-changed

The I<sort-column-changed> signal is emitted when the sort column
or sort order of C<$sortable> is changed. The signal is emitted before
the contents of C<$sortable> are resorted.

=begin code
method handler (
  Int :$_handle_id,
  N-GObject :$_native-object,
  Gnome::Gtk4::TreeSortable :$_widget,
  *%user-options
)
=end code

=item $_handle_id; The registered event handler id.
=item $_native-object; The native object provided by the Raku object which registered this event. This is a native B<Gnome::Gtk4::TreeSortable> object.
=item %user-options; A list of named arguments provided by L<.register-signal() in class Object|/content-docs/api2/reference/GObject/Object#register-signal>.

